{"type": "article", "id": 30355, "title": "魔方书架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-31T22:57:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 207, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160731211443yNelw4kM1AOgSTnJ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>当你第一眼看到空空的 <a href=\"http://anesis.com.gr/en/portfolio/bookcase-rubika/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rubika B601</a> 时，或许还以为它出自某位 3D 绘画师的笔下。它实际上是设计师 George Bosnas 借鉴了鲁比克魔方的造型为希腊品牌 <a href=\"http://anesis.com.gr/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anesis</a> 设计的一款六边形书架，独特的菱形格子不仅可以摆放书籍也可以用来摆放酒瓶、盆栽或是其他装饰品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731212602kzyCNPY5ltJ942mE.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731212601Wf0tSbCZgD36P8kK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731212602thxW1yTIsXUavcZ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731212601HScPFrmpvixB9k0n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}